# Copy to .env and fill in. .env is gitignored — never commit a real key.
#
# Google Cloud (same project as the key):
#   - Enable Places API (New) and Routes API
#   - Billing on the project ($200/mo free credit applies)
#   - Credentials → restrict this key to Places API (New) + Routes API only
#   - Do not use this key in index.html or any deployed static files;
#     enrich + the local admin editor read it from .env server-side only.
GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your-key-here
